## INTEGRATION WITH OTHER PLAYBOOKS

- **`marc-facts.md`** — pull scope/credibility hooks for Marc’s self-description. “Senior Lead PM on embedded products at ADP, owned PLG strategy that beat plan 25%” is tighter than “PM at ADP.”
- **`resume-tailoring.md`** — if Marc has tailored to a specific company’s JD recently, outreach to people there should reference the same positioning as the resume. Consistency across channels.
- **`fact-capture.md`** — relationship facts are not facts (too volatile). Specific affiliations are (e.g., “Marc’s Cornell Johnson cohort includes [name] at [company]” if it’s reusable intel). Only capture if Marc confirms and it’ll matter for future outreach.
- **`resume-teardown.md`** — unrelated. Do not invoke for outreach.

